OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives offer home tax
OL,4,Cdeal to back Labour budget
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives have suggested
OL,7,Fthey will support a Labour budget if
OL,8,Fthe devolved government backs its
OL,9,Fplans to scrap a tax paid by
OL,10,Fhomebuyers.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, the Welsh Government will
OL,13,Foutline its spending plans for the
OL,14,Fnext financial year.
OL,16,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan has
OL,17,Falready warned of cuts to frontline
OL,18,Fservices if her Labour government does
OL,19,Fnot succeed in passing a budget.
