OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives offer home tax
OL,4,Cdeal to back Labour budget
OL,6,F"Our ambition to scrap stamp duty in
OL,7,FWales as part of our plan to fix
OL,8,FWales, will help people get onto the
OL,9,Fhousing ladder, improve mobility in
OL,10,Fthe housing market, and boost the
OL,11,Feconomy.
OL,13,F"It will be central to any discussions
OL,14,Fwhich may now take place."
OL,16,FAt the Conservative Party conference
OL,17,Fearlier this month, Kemi Badenoch
OL,18,Fpromised to abolish stamp duty if the
OL,19,FConservatives win the next election.
